    <item>
      <title>銀座であんみつ</title>
      <link>https://tokyo-dragon-road.net/post/2023/anmitsu-ginza/</link>
      <pubDate>Sun, 24 Dec 2023 23:22:21 +0900</pubDate>
      <guid>https://tokyo-dragon-road.net/post/2023/anmitsu-ginza/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;大分前の訪問だけど、銀座若松のあんみつ。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://tokyo-dragon-road.net/img/2023/ginza-anmitsu_2735.JPG&#34; alt=&#34;あんみつ&#34;&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;https://tokyo-dragon-road.net/img/2023/ginza-anmitsu_2734.JPG&#34; alt=&#34;あんみつ&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
