&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://tokyo-dragon-road.net/img/2023/olive_170_1989_%E3%83%AC%E3%83%92%E3%82%9A%E3%83%83%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A5_2879.jpeg&#34; alt=&#34;Olive&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://tokyo-dragon-road.net/img/2023/olive_170_1989_biore_2844.jpg&#34; alt=&#34;Olive&#34;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
